2026-05-15T01:32:01.2401167Z 13    <!--
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2401743Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2402639Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2404141Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2405051Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2406069Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2406803Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
