2026-05-15T01:32:01.2410461Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2411222Z 22    <!--
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2412014Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2412740Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2413394Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2414249Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2415071Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2415883Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2416703Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2417529Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2418696Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2419473Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2420065Z 33    -->
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2420688Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2421742Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-15T01:32:01.2422829Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
